    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023400/extras/9611c6443e4415e8b276d9f302c2d1c9.avif?t=1749023581\" width=600 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Ferdinand fight <strong>climate change</strong> and the <strong>government</strong> while caring for his <strong>mental health</strong> in this <strong>minigame compilation</strong>!<br>Choose <strong>actions</strong> to take based on your <strong>resource</strong> need and get ready to <strong>mash</strong> your keyboard or controller. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3023400/extras/244b8e24a0517457a107d2c6614619ee.avif?t=1749023581\" width=600 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 More than 100 short burst <strong>minigames</strong> inspired by real life <br>🪧 A <strong>corrupted capitalist government</strong> that does not care about climate change <br>💥 Some <strong>ecoterrorism</strong> here and there (depending on your definition) <br>📱 <strong>Scrolling</strong> social medias  <br>🍝 A <strong>recipe</strong> for pesto pastas <br>🖥️ Making a <strong>video game</strong>  <br>⭐ and much more!   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> <br>This game is made for the <strong>Nintendo Game Boy Advance</strong> and will be run on your computer through the<strong> mGBA emulator</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Despite having a lot of <strong>minigames</strong> the game is only made by a <strong>single person</strong> and is <strong>fairly short</strong>.</p>",
